summary: Since it’s Mental Health Awareness Month/Week Can I just say a big thank you to Dan Howell, for not only posting his Daniel and...
body:
Since it’s Mental Health Awareness Month/Week

Can I just say a big thank you to Dan Howell, for not only posting his Daniel and Depression video back in 2017, but also continuing to be an advocate for Mental Health?

Thanks to your video, not only did you open my eyes and help me understand what my mother and sister are going through, but it also helped me understand my own issues

So again, thank you Dan, not only for that video but for everything

P.S

Also Phil, because of your “Try New Things” motto, it helped me me push forward and finally get work in a place I love and enjoy

So thank you!
